response.original_title: Nicki Doane: Maya Yoga Vinyasa Fusion - Core Strength Flow Series 1
response.overview: Fitness expert and yoga instructor Nicki Doane leads this release, combining the practices of Asana -- yoga poses, with Pranayama -- conscious breathing. Fusing the two traditions into a single routine, the program aims to focus attention on the toning and strengthening of the core muscles in the mid-section and back. Cammila Collar, Rovi
